Name: Neko Navy
About the game: Flying cats versus 10,000 soothing characters! What awaits them beyond all those furious midair fights...? Witness the world's most shocking ending for yourself! Shoot, evade, and detonate Bombers! Neko Navy is an exhilarating horizontal-scrolling shooter with easy controls. The game offers three difficulties that everyone from a beginner to an advanced player can enjoy. Fire off as many Bombers as you can to achieve high scores! Features Horizontal single-player shoot'em'up 7 Stages 3 Difficulties (EASY, HARD, DEATH) 6 Playable cats(?) Soundtrack included
